title: Franchise Tag Deadline, Josh Rosen Rumors with Sean Wagner (Football 3/6)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner to break down all the guys who were franchise tagged by various NFL teams, to examine the market for the guys who weren't tagged and to discuss the latest NFL news. Then the guys break down the latest Josh Rosen rumors and where he might go in a possible trade, plus some mock draft discussions. 
BREAK: 32:11
